(1319, 2079, '2012-05-15 18:10:45.673', N'Alenanno', '2014-07-27 12:00:49.967', NULL, NULL, NULL, N'<p>I"m a student majoring in Languages (branch: Linguistics), currently working as a freelance translator. I"ve recently discovered <a href="http://db.tt/WpiKeReH" rel="nofollow">Dropbox</a> and I"m going to use it for my needs! :)</p>    <p><strong><em>I love</em></strong><br>  Languages, Movies (Fantasy, Sci-Fi, Tarantino, etc.), Music, 3D Graphics, books and so on. </p>    <p>Appointed ♦ Moderator Pro Tempore on <a href="http://area51.stackexchange.com/proposals/6673/linguistics?referrer=GlDGLdkDYNxMg1X13CJ1vg2">Linguistics SE</a>, <a href="http://area51.stackexchange.com/proposals/6388/chinese-language-usage?referrer=XzTG1Nz01tc01sJEhak_6g2">Chinese SE</a> and the <a href="http://area51.stackexchange.com/proposals/10848/russian-language-usage?referrer=J7IYS3ZUomUDvVVb-6SmDQ2">Russian SE</a> site. If you"re interested in other Stack Exchanges, try the <a href="http://area51.stackexchange.com/proposals/42949/italian-language-usage?referrer=ALVtGpK0tjLp1Lw15QCaUA2">Italian SE</a> site.</p>    <p>I like to lurk on other sites" Metas. <em>Meta is fun!</em> </p>    <p><strong>My feature requests</strong>:</p>    <ol>  <li><a href="http://meta.stackexchange.com/q/135786/176533">Alert a moderator when an answer is improved after a post notice</a></li>  <li><a href="http://meta.stackexchange.com/q/138273/176533">Automatically add chat event to the community bulletin (or make it easier)</a></li>  <li><a href="http://meta.stackexchange.com/q/121363/176533">Give 10k users the ability to see the total count of flags they"ve handled</a></li>  </ol>    <p><strong>Moderator issues</strong>: If you have concerns or want to contact me about my moderation, you can find/ping me either in the <a href="http://chat.stackexchange.com/rooms/1336/linguistics">Linguistics SE chat room</a> or <a href="http://chat.stackexchange.com/rooms/1984/chinese-language-and-usage">CL&amp;U chat room</a>